r: rgb(74, 74, 74); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">　　枫藏艺术平台由数字藏品行业应用服务商藏文网络科技打造出品，定位为行业数字藏品项目孵化与数字版权交易平台。枫藏艺术平台将深耕服务于各行业品牌的数字藏品发行、交易，联合各文化艺术企业、IP运营方、数藏发行方，立足于数字艺术产业的发展，以虚促实，为国内外品牌企业提供数字衍生品发行等配套服务。</span></p></section></section><section style="margin: 1.2em 0px 0px; padding: 1em; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(214, 58, 49); border-radius: 8px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-brushtype="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(214, 58, 49); text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">购买须知</strong></span></section><section style="margin: 12px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(214, 58, 49); height: 1px; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section data-brushtype="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(214, 58, 49); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">　　“枫藏”艺术平台在保护艺术家艺术作品数字版权的基础上，实现真实可信的数字与实体艺术品的发行、收藏和使用。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">　　1、仅限实名认证为年满18周岁的中国大陆用户购买。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">　　2、艺术作品的版权由艺术家或艺术机构所有，用户除获得版权方的书面同意以外，不得将艺术作品用于任何商业用途，包括但不限于出售艺术作品的副本、使用权、衍生作品。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">　　3、“枫藏”艺术平台销售的数字形态的艺术作品一经售出，不支持退换。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">　　4、请勿对艺术作品进行炒作、场外交易、欺诈，或以任何其他非法方式进行使用。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.7546875" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/RGVeicC0CVNX8BCXVRumVUH7lFDZ3Rk7GBWJibLiaRqnJ5UicHwM7pwkNuymzzVL8SAkzfSybFIqbfC9t5BfIBpP5Q/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="640" data-imgqrcoded="1" data-imgid="0.38123935331477976" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; caret-color: red; width: 578px; height: auto !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></p></section></section>', '2022-07-07 09:59:20', 0, 1);
